        <div class="content">
            <div class="container-fluid">
              <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:30px">
                    <div class="col-md-100">
                            <div class="header">
                                <p class="category">The objective of this analysis is to identify how much support MISST related studies get and to analyze trends to understand how these tools are used in research.</p>
                                <p class="category">A keyword-based approach was taken to uncover trends related to a predefined list of keywords</p>
